Package: doe.gov
Title: DOE Energy Data eXchange (EDX) API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the DOE Energy Data eXchange (EDX) CKAN API at edx.netl.doe.gov. Covers dataset search, individual dataset metadata, resource listings, tag browsing, and dataset counts across 18000+ energy research datasets.
